### Recommended Test Order
1. `POST /api/users` → create admin user (no auth needed for first user)
2. `POST /api/auth/login` → get token
3. `POST /api/guests` → create guest profile (uses userId from step 1)
4. `POST /api/room-types` → create room type
5. `POST /api/rooms` → create room (uses roomTypeId)
6. `POST /api/rate-plans` → create rate plan (uses roomTypeId)
7. `POST /api/reservations` → create reservation (uses guestId, roomTypeId, ratePlanId)
8. `POST /api/stays/check-in` → check in (uses reservationId, guestId, roomId)
9. `POST /api/folio-items` → post charges (uses stayId)
10. `PATCH /api/stays/1/check-out` → check out

